import React from "react";
import { Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input, FormText } from "reactstrap";

const DeployForm = () => {
  return (
    <Form>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="Model-Name">Model Name</Label>
        <Input
          type="text"
          name="Model-Name"
          id="modelname"
          placeholder="model-name"
        />
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="description">Description</Label>
        <Input
          type="text"
          name="description"
          id="description"
          placeholder="Description"
        />
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="diseases">Select Diseases</Label>
        <Input type="select" name="diseases" id="diseases" multiple>
          <option>1</option>
          <option>2</option>
          <option>3</option>
          <option>4</option>
          <option>5</option>
        </Input>
      </FormGroup>
      <Button>Submit</Button>
    </Form>
  );
};

export default DeployForm;
